8.2 Scenario 
Feature: EXPERIENCE ITINERARY TABLE 
Then: Users want to establish experience ITINERARY 
Then: If activity moves through out different Location.
Then: User clicks to Add ITINERARY TABLE 
Then: ACTIVITY ITINERARY TABLE opens 
And: Already Titled as the EXPERIENCE NAME from above.
Then. Organizer add 1 STAGE NAME by its LOCATION.
Then: System should be linked to MAP DATA BASE (GOOGLE MAP)
Then: User can clicks directly on the map to add LOCATION NAME to the 1 STAGE
And: Sytem acn autocomplete the name of location at the gap typed by Organizer
Then: Systen finds a match at MAP And LOCATION Data base
Then: Then 1 STAGE at itinerary table now displays with EXACT location name 
And: An ubication signal get ATTACHED TO MAP at location. 
Then: User will now clicks in the 1 STAGE to add brief stage description 100 characters
Then: STAGE will only show the name of LOCATION SELECTED
aND: Only by placing mose on stage at map you get dilog text with brief description.
Then: By cliking on the stage days number
then : Organizer can add number of days spent at that stage
Then: FOR EACH DAY seleccted sytem will show the indpendently
And: organizer will marck 3 categories histogram with / value of activity desired.  
Then: Oranizer will Giving each day a % at different categories.
Then: User add % of that day dedicated to Sport, Nature, Landscapes & Sightseeing. 
And: User add % of that day dedicated to Relax, free time or Mind Activities. 
And: User add % of that day dedicated to People, Culture & Gastronomy. 
Then: TOTAL DAY VALUE DAY will show sumatory % values at any given time
And: as soon as any % value is added by orginazer to the categories 
Then; Sytem will add inmediatly value to total day % value gap below.
And: system wont allow more than 100% at total sumatory or categories gap
Then: System will always place actumatically % value for last category 
And: Until compleate 100& of day value.
And: IN case organizer not agree with last valued added
Then: Organizer can cliks on top of any category to change its value.
And: Adding a new % value to it, autoomatically wil delivery differnt value to other categries.
Then: Addin or deduce from categories half excess or deficit till 100 value for total day
Then: till each category is rated an total sumatory is 100%
( example:1DAY= Adventure 60% + Relax 20% + Culture 20%= total 100%
(Then if %value introduce in that order sytem would add 20% for cultre)
Then: System will now show an PIE CHART FOR EACH DAY AT ITINERARY TABLE STAGES
And: pie chart will be added to the STAGE for EACH DAY 
And : display at ITINERARY TABLE FOR ACTIVITY OFFER

